      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $n \\in \\N^*$, $\\omega = e^{2i\\pi/n}$ et\n$Z = \\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}\\,\\omega^{k^2}$. On demande de calculer $|Z|^2$.\nPour cela $\\ldots$",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n \\in \\N^*\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\omega = e^{2i\\pi/n}\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Z = \\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}\\,\\omega^{k^2}\\)</span>. On demande de calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(|Z|^2\\)</span>. Pour cela <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\ldots\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5958a9c8-06f3-4a6a-919c-f1280ed6d24d",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "{\\'E}crire $|Z|^2$ comme une somme double.",
        "html": "<p><span>É</span>crire <span class=\"math inline\">\\(|Z|^2\\)</span> comme une somme double.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "50502db5-31fd-45a3-8a63-663ce8ad0f82",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Regrouper les termes diagonalement en tenant compte de la p{\\'e}riodicit{\\'e} de\n    la fonction $k \\mapsto \\omega^k$.",
        "html": "<p>Regrouper les termes diagonalement en tenant compte de la p<span>é</span>riodicit<span>é</span> de la fonction <span class=\"math inline\">\\(k \\mapsto \\omega^k\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "d63b28be-e1bd-4ec9-b70d-03c5bef3e042",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Terminer le calcul.",
        "html": "<p>Terminer le calcul.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "1a14e323-37cd-4df3-b5c1-76929dc23657",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$n$ impair $ \\Rightarrow  |Z|^2 = n$,\\par\n         $n$ pair $ \\Rightarrow  |Z|^2 = n(1+(-1)^{n/2})$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span> impair <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Rightarrow  |Z|^2 = n\\)</span>,</p>\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span> pair <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Rightarrow  |Z|^2 = n(1+(-1)^{n/2})\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
